{"title": "Law of the Four Just Men", "description": "The first six of the stories in this collection were originally published under the title \"Some Adventures of the Four Just Men\" in The Strand Magazine in 1921. This collection of stories is practically a portmanteau. Each story is complete within its own chapter, but there are small links between them that bring them together. Time has moved on for our Just men; Poiccart seems to be on semi-permanent hiatus on his farm in France, but Manfred and Gonsalez venture out from their flat in Jermyn Street to meet challenges wrought by the criminal fraternity. - Summary by Andy Sames", "duration": 21430, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "2079", "name": "Edgar Wallace"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/lawofthefourjustmen_2602_librivox/lawofthefourjustmen_2602.jpg", "copyright_year": "1921", "genres": ["Detective Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Andy Sames"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Andy Sames"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "DaveC"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "mleigh"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "The Man Who Lived at Clapham", "readers": [7532], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/lawofthefourjustmen_2602_librivox/lawofthefourjustmen_01_wallace_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2409}, {"section": 2, "title": "The Man With the Canine Teeth", "readers": [7532], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/lawofthefourjustmen_2602_librivox/lawofthefourjustmen_02_wallace_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2367}, {"section": 3, "title": "The Man Who Hated Earthworms", "readers": [7532], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/lawofthefourjustmen_2602_librivox/lawofthefourjustmen_03_wallace_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1744}, {"section": 4, "title": "The Man Who Died Twice", "readers": [7532], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/lawofthefourjustmen_2602_librivox/lawofthefourjustmen_04_wallace_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1797}, {"section": 5, "title": "The Man Who